00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:58,000
Guys, can we just play?
伙计们 打牌好吗?

706
00:35:58,500 --> 00:35:59,700
I'm trying.
我尽量

707
00:36:01,300 --> 00:36:02,100
Fine.
好吧

708
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:04,500
Deal.
该你了

709
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,200
Hello?
喂?

710
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:15,100
Mr. Scavo,
Scavo先生

711
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:16,900
It's Lamar from the Limo service.
我是Limo服务公司的Lamar

712
00:36:16,900 --> 00:36:18,700
Uh, I got a flat,
我的车子坏了

713
00:36:18,700 --> 00:36:21,000
So I might be late picking up you and your wife.
所以我可能会晚点去接你和你太太

714
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:23,100
What are you talking about? I-I-I canceled you.
你在说什么啊? 我...我不是跟你取消了吗

715
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:26,300
No, you didn't. Yes, I did. I left you a message.
- 不 你没有 - 我有的 我有留言给你啊

716
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:27,600
Oh, I must have missed it.
噢 我一定是没收到

717
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:30,600
Anyway, I dropped your wife off, right where you told me.
总之呢 我把你妻子放在你告诉我的地方了

718
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:32,200
Oh, god. When?
噢 上帝啊 什么时候的事?

719
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,300
About two hours ago.
大概两小时前

720
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:42,500
Guys, um, lock up when you're done.
伙计们 你们完事儿锁好门

721
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:47,793
I'll open.
我先来

722
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,000
I'm out.
不跟

723
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:52,600
And I'll raise you.
我加钱

724
00:36:57,900 --> 00:36:58,800
You want a beer?
你要啤酒吗

725
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:01,400
Hell, Tom's gone. Let's go open up the good stuff.
该死 Tome走了 我们自己去找点好东西吧

726
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:06,900
Well...
恩...

727
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:08,900
Looks like it's just you and me,
看来就剩下咱俩了

728
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:11,200
<i>If you're still in.
如果你还继续的话</i>

729
00:37:12,300 --> 00:37:14,600
With this hand? You bet I am.
这一手牌? 当然了

730
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,700
I'll re-raise.
我再加

731
00:37:25,900 --> 00:37:27,400
And raise again.
再加

732
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:33,000
Your stack's looking kinda small.
你的筹码看起来少了点

733
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,600
Will you taka check?
你收支票吗

734
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:46,500
You know I can't match that.
你知道我没钱继续跟

735
00:37:47,900 --> 00:37:49,300
How about this, then?
那这样好不好

736
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:51,200
You win, you keep the money,
你赢了 钱都归你

737
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:53,100
And you tell Susan whatever you want.
你还可以把你想说的都告诉Susan

738
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:57,000
I win, you keep your mouth shut about the ring,
我赢了 你就再也不许提戒指的事

739
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,900
And you leave me and Susan alone.
并且离我和Susan远远的

740
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:13,300
Deal.
成交

741
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:29,300
How was the game?
牌打得怎样

742
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:31,700
I won.
我赢了

743
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:48,600
Lynette, I am so sorry. I am so sorry!
Lynette 我很抱歉 对不起

744
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:52,600
You see, there was supposed to be a horse-drawn carriage and--
瞧 这本该是有一辆马车的...

745
00:38:54,600 --> 00:38:56,400
Oh, good. You got the flowers.
噢 很好 你收到花了

746
00:39:10,200 --> 00:39:11,000
Coffee?
咖啡?

747
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,100
Yes, please.
是的 谢谢

748
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:16,900
Yeah, she-- She likes coffee, too. Thanks.
是的 她...她也要咖啡 谢谢

749
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,784
I'm really, really,really sorry...
我真的真的很...

750
00:39:21,972 --> 00:39:24,300
Please stop apologizing.
不要再道歉了

751
00:39:24,300 --> 00:39:26,300
I'm s-- I appreciate what you were trying to do.
- 我... - 我很感激你原本想要做的

752
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,100
It was a lovely though
很美好的想法

753
00:39:27,100 --> 00:39:30,600
<i>That just went hideously, hideously, hideously wrong.
只是结果变的非常非常非常糟糕</i>

754
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:35,500
Wait till the kids find out that you saw a real coyote.
孩子要是知道你见过活的郊狼的话....

755
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:36,600
Hideously.
还是糟糕

756
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,800
Well, I learned my lesson.
好吧 我得到教训了

757
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,900
Never again. No more surprises.
再也不要想制造惊喜

758
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:47,400
From now on, I'll do exactly what you say.
从现在开始 我就完全按照你说的去做

759
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:55,200
Oh, don't. You... dare.
噢 你...你敢

760
00:39:56,200 --> 00:39:57,000
What?
什么?

761
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:00,100
I had a lot of time to think tonight,
我想了很久今晚的事

762
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:02,017
And I realized you were right.
我想你是对的

763
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:05,367
We have to keep the romance going,
我们要保持浪漫

764
00:40:05,900 --> 00:40:07,900
No matter how tired we are.
不管我们有多累

765
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:12,500
The only thing worse thaor just going through the motions
比光想不做更糟糕的是

766
00:40:12,500 --> 00:40:16,239
Is not bothering to go through the motions.
连想都不肯想

767
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:20,500
So you want me to surprise you next year?
那么 你希望我明年也给你准备惊喜?

768
00:40:21,700 --> 00:40:23,000
Knock yourself out.
让你自己吃惊吧

769
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:26,700
Just wait, 'cause I will think of something even better.
你就等着吧 因为我会构思出更好的主意

770
00:40:26,700 --> 00:40:28,300
Well, after this year,
有了今年这回

771
00:40:28,300 --> 00:40:30,900
I would be happy with any date
任何约会都够让我开心的了

772
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:33,056
That included food and shelter.
只要有吃有住就行

773
00:40:46,300 --> 00:40:47,200
Nine years.
9年纪念快乐

774
00:40:52,300 --> 00:40:53,400
Nine years...
9年快乐

775
00:40:54,900 --> 00:40:57,000
And I have loved every minute of it.
每一份钟我都没有停止过爱你

776
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:00,500
Me, too.
我也是

777
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:12,300
<i>(Rex) take a drive down any street in suburbia.
在郊区的任何一条街上开车</i>

778
00:41:12,700 --> 00:41:14,000
<i>Know what you're gonna see?
知道你会看到什么吗?</i>

779
00:41:16,100 --> 00:41:18,900
<i>A bunch of guys wearing the same expression.
有着同样表情的一群男人们 </i>

780
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:22,200
<i>It's a look that says,
那表情在说</i>

781
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:24,000
<i>"Oh, crap.
"噢 该死"</i>

782
00:41:24,700 --> 00:41:27,000
<i>My dreams are never gonna come true."
"我的梦想永远不会实现了"</i>

783
00:41:30,700 --> 00:41:33,500
<i>"I'll never have a life free from scandal."
"我永远无法摆脱这种荒谬的生活了"</i>

784
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:38,200
<i>"I'll never have a son of my own."
"我永远不会有自己的儿子了"</i>

785
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:43,300
<i>"I'll never hold her in my arms again."
"我再也无法拥她入怀了"</i>

786
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:49,949
<i>"I'll never get to tell her how I feel."
我永远也没有机会告诉她我的感受了</i>

787
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:57,999
<i>Yeah, the suburbs are filled with a lot of men who have given up hope.
的确 在郊区的男人有很多都放弃了希望</i>

788
00:42:00,200 --> 00:42:03,900
<i>Of course, every once in a while you do come across some lucky S.O.B.
当然偶尔 你会碰到那种走运的家伙</i>

789
00:42:03,972 --> 00:42:06,283
<i>whose dreams have all come true.
他的梦想可以成真</i>

790
00:42:08,486 --> 00:42:10,072
<i>You know how you spot them?
你知道怎样能认出他们吗?</i>

791
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:14,334
<i>They're the ones who can't stop smiling.
那些脸上止不住笑容的人</i>

792
00:42:16,700 --> 00:42:19,619
<i>Don't you just hate those guys?
这种人是不是让你觉得很可恨?</i>

